add support to keywords "meta"
<input>
skill {
  name: Simple Skill
  meta {
    attr1: attribute 1
    attr2: attribute 2
    ...
  }
}
</input>
<output>
---
name: "Simple Skill"
meta:
attr1: "attriute 1"
attr2: "attriute 2"
...
---
</output>
the meta can contain N attributes, like attr3, attr4...
